tasks.description:
## AC
- Run harvest-sync-fuseki.sh to push Drive photo + music TTL files to Fuseki
- SPARQL query confirms Drive photos visible: SELECT (COUNT(*) AS ?n) WHERE { ?p jb:photoSource 'google-drive' }
- SPARQL query confirms Drive music visible: SELECT (COUNT(*) AS ?n) WHERE { ?t jb:musicSource 'google-drive' }
- No OOM or timeout during sync
- Verify /photos and /music API endpoints return Drive items
